			<name>
				<baseName xml:lang="en">Spodumene（0.7% Li2O）</baseName>
				<baseName xml:lang="zh">锂辉石（0.7%氧化锂）</baseName>
			</name>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="en">Triphane</common:synonyms>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="zh">Triphane</common:synonyms>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification name="ILCD 1.1" classes="../ILCDClassification.xml">
					<common:class level="0">Materials production</common:class>
					<common:class level="1">Other mineralic materials</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Spodumene is a pyroxene member of inosilicate mineral with lithium aluminium. It can be pink, lilac, or green. Crystals are prismatic, flattened, and typically striated along their length. Gem varieties of the mineral usually exhibit strong pleochroism. Spodumene is an important ore of lithium. It belongs to the pyroxene group of minerals and has a monoclinic crystal structure. Its lattice is characterised by unequal axes, making it easy to identify because of its angles. Spodumene is then transformed into lithium chemical salts.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">锂辉石是一种含锂铝的非硅酸盐矿物，属于辉石类。它可以呈粉红色、淡紫色或绿色。晶体呈棱柱状，扁平，通常沿其长度方向呈条纹状。该矿物的宝石品种通常表现出强烈的多色性。钠长石是一种重要的锂矿石。它属于辉石类矿物，具有单斜晶体结构。其晶格的特征是不等轴，因此很容易从角度上识别。正长岩可转化为锂化学盐。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>LiAlSi2O6</sumFormula>
